{"tid":1435869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「文宣討論」提升釋放義士訴求的支持度","createTime":"2019-08-09T07:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T07:33:01.000Z","uid":8948,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"654a778cb18581316b2197247eb261874e536615","tid":1435869,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:13:30.000Z","msg":"首先我好希望成場運動大家都堅持五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n但作為一個現實主義者，如果某一個訴求係冇民意支持既話，最終係好容易被放棄<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我認為呢刻有必要，集中做文宣提升「釋放義士」呢一個訴求既支持度</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQ3VhPn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQ3VhPn.png&h=144ccbf2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n睇返民意研究所既報告<br />\n<br />\n釋放被捕人士既支持度係連<span style=\"color: red;\">50％</span>都唔夠，呢個最貼身影響抗爭力量既訴求既支持度<br />\n竟然連要林鄭下台都比唔上<br />\n<br />\n希望呢個post大家可以brain storm 下，有咩理據可以拎黎做文宣說服其他人支持呢一個訴求<br />\n<br />\n首先睇睇對家提出乜野理據<br />\n1。她又提到示威者提出的5大訴求中，其中要求特區政府釋放被捕人士，但近日示威者製造炸藥、持大量攻擊性武器等違法行為，反問「係咪全部都要唔追究」，希望大家每一次提出五大訴求，要想一想這是否法治社會可以爭取的。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">反駁：政府承認修例工作完全失敗，但未有負上任何責任<br />\n再者政府承認失敗後，卻繼續以不同罪名追究 以血汗揭露政府腐敗的年輕人<br />\n企圖滅聲</span><br />\n<br />\n2。作為行政長官冇權去撤銷控罪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">律政司直接聽命於行政長官，而檢控守則寫明檢控應考慮是否符合公眾利益<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190629/20716280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F20716280&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzUYzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=f14f5291\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F20716280&h=271c8d2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190629/20716280</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3。基本法下，檢控由律政司司長獨立進行<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n反駁：律政司檢控專員公開信，指律政司只考慮政治因素<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190801/20741243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F20741243&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzUYzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=7e932cef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190801%2F20741243&h=2b00f09b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190801/20741243</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係以上都係比較複雜既理據，想咁多位巴絲打提出唔同簡潔既理據／創意去整文宣<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落，一個都不能少</span></span><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n【教學】自己文宣自己整，人人都係文宣組，教你量產文宣圖（2）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426420</a>"},{"pid":"b2863e049c4f75f0498abb12d4fd1bfe7e36c674","tid":1435869,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"899ef1a182fc578b4a1537dd15223106b2e71b75","tid":1435869,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:15:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57f4796e42ab0da8e753e07f6e760c1979f71bc6","tid":1435869,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f178e56947f1b0aa841a5e06a4d3940b54aec97e","tid":1435869,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:16:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b887b31701b323603d67b7476cb603570e1d82e2","tid":1435869,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:16:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3288c900f94da749cd4673f6da9a527fffc772ed","tid":1435869,"uid":191688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"開返個五毛回覆範本有冇得諗？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435787</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"046ef5c06245